    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/actor/vv40-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single-condition testing; this shortfall is accepted because the COU is restricted to the single ASTM F1717 configuration tested and no extrapolation is claimed. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium assurance level determination. The validation results generated under configuration ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 are considered applicable to the production model ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7 on the basis of the internal equivalence review (CCR-2026-0312), without re-execution of the validation suite.",
